类 SupperVTDGenHuge

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ximpleware.extended.VTDGenHuge
      • com.ximpleware.extended.SupperVTDGenHuge

  • public class SupperVTDGenHuge
extends com.ximpleware.extended.VTDGenHuge
    VTDGenHuge implementation supporting extended VTD (256GB file size). Current support built-in entities only It parses DTD, but doesn't resolve declared entities
